[32m+[m[32m## 📊 Understanding the Data[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### LiDAR Data (Point Clouds)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**What it is:** Millions of 3D points representing the environment[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**ROS Topics:**[m
[32m+[m[32m- `/unilidar/cloud` - Raw LiDAR data[m
[32m+[m[32m- `/cloud_registered` - SLAM-processed data[m
[32m+[m[32m- `/Odometry` - Robot position[m
[32m+[m[32m- `/path` - Movement trajectory[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**View in real-time:**[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32m# LiDAR publishes automatically when running[m
[32m+[m[32mros2 topic hz /unilidar/cloud        # Check rate (~10 Hz)[m
[32m+[m[32mros2 topic echo /Odometry            # See position[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Camera Data (Images)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**What it is:** 1920x1080 images, dual fisheye format[m
