[32m+[m[32m## 🛠️ Troubleshooting[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### LiDAR Not Working[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Symptom:** No point cloud in RViz, or not mapping[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Checks:**[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32m# 1. Verify connection[m
[32m+[m[32mls /dev/ttyUSB*           # Should see /dev/ttyUSB0[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# 2. Check status[m
[32m+[m[32m./unitree_lidar_L1 status[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# 3. Test LiDAR only[m
[32m+[m[32m./unitree_lidar_L1 run[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Common fixes:**[m
[32m+[m[32m- Unplug and replug LiDAR USB cable[m
[32m+[m[32m- Check LiDAR power indicator light[m
[32m+[m[32m- Ensure clear 360° view (no obstructions)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Move around** - SLAM needs motion to initialize[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Camera Not Detected[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Symptom:** Camera not found by `test_insta360.sh`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Checks:**[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32m# 1. Verify camera connected[m
[32m+[m[32mlsusb | grep -i insta[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# 2. Check USB mode[m
[32m+[m[32m# Camera must be in "USB Webcam" mode, NOT "Mass Storage"[m
[32m+[m[32m# On camera: Settings → USB Mode → USB Webcam[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# 3. Test after reconnecting[m
[32m+[m[32m./test_insta360.sh[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Common fixes:**[m
[32m+[m[32m- Switch camera to "USB Webcam" mode[m
[32m+[m[32m- Unplug and replug USB cable[m
[32m+[m[32m- Try different USB port[m
[32m+[m[32m- Check camera battery is charged[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Point-LIO Not Initializing[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Symptom:** LiDAR running but no map building[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Solution:**[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Move the sensor!** Point-LIO needs motion to initialize[m
[32m+[m[32m- Point at feature-rich environment (corners, objects)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Avoid blank walls or empty rooms[m
[32m+[m[32m- Give it 5-10 seconds while moving[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
